{"tid":228760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"甄子丹、成龍PK誰強？徐曉冬秒選：成龍只是個演員","createTime":"2017-05-04T06:38:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T04:51:23.000Z","uid":64544,"like":106,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1cd4a5652a17383f930daf779ec9c730ead5226f","tid":228760,"uid":64544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T06:38:42.000Z","msg":"北京「格鬥狂人」徐曉冬因花20秒不到時間，就擊倒大陸太極宗師魏雷，引發各界熱議。<span style=\"color: red;\">他近日被網友問及「甄子丹和成龍PK，誰比較強？」他毫不猶豫回答甄子丹，直言「成龍就是個演員。」</span><br />\n<br />\n被網友封為「格鬥狂人」的徐曉冬，近日也持續收到許多戰帖，其中包括少林、峨眉、青城、崑崙、崆峒、武當等，面臨如此多派系的挑戰，他不但沒有卻步，反而全都答應，「我覺得他們就是假的，我必須要打。」<br />\n<br />\n然而，徐曉冬一戰成名後，網友也紛紛提出問題，有人問「這次搏擊vs太極最大的意義是什麼？」他回答「真實打破神話。」此外，還有人好奇詢問「你覺得成龍和甄子丹巔峰時期誰更能打？」徐毫不猶豫選擇了甄子丹，並解釋「甄子丹，正經練過，成龍就是個演員。」<br />\n<img src=\"http://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/05/03/895688-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F05%2F03%2F895688-XXL.jpg&h=b670ac16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=249449\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D249449&d=fL1pPRntFf1zvvLBqslw3r%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=9ed2e169\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D249449&h=e7815c11\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=249449</a>"},{"pid":"fc287b03ec37c2620cd381580b3506e5efc8ccb0","tid":228760,"uid":64544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T06:44:01.000Z","msg":"宇宙最強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c95b0477fd927761f18483786b0cd93a907ad82","tid":228760,"uid":64544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:15:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://referentiel.nouvelobs.com/file/15773076-10-choses-a-savoir-sur-do